    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-04-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-04-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="41" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d41">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-04-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 18,
                                1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson telegraphs that according to intelligence received from the
                            south the revolutionary cause has been abandoned by Admiral Mello, who
                            has gone with 1,200 men and 4 vessels of the revolting squadron to the
                            Argentine Republic, which gives them protection. The sinking of the <hi rend="italic">Aqnidaban</hi> and the complete overthrow of the
                            revolutionary movement are announced.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
